    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Parse receipts with Google Drive and MySQL hands-free for OCR & Extraction\n\n**Pattern:** File Processing · **Level:** Foundation · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nParse receipts with Google Drive and MySQL hands-free for OCR & Extraction. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual ocr & extraction is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nDaily Schedule → Download from Google Drive → Parse CSV Contents → Clean & Reshape Rows → Load Rows into MySQL → Stamp Processing Time → Guard Non-Empty fileName → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to file processing without manual effort\n- Anyone automating ocr & extraction in legal\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n- Responds in seconds\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2; MySQL connection.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -830,
        80
      ],
